snippet.title: ✨ Life After Magic - Steam Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Can you save magic before the clock strikes midnight on New Year’s Eve? Life After Magic is a queer, retro visual novel that follows jaded ex-magical girls as they reconnect, deal with young adulthood, and face off against one last threat before Y2K hits.

Available now, free forever!

Search for “Life After Magic” on Steam and Itch.io
